  "prompt": "What is the best site to download Hindi music for free?",
  "response": "Downloading Hindi music for free can be a challenge due to legal and ethical concerns surrounding distribution rights. However, there are several sites where you can access Hindi music legally and often for free, depending on their policies. Some of these include:\n\n1. **JioSaavn**: This site offers a vast collection of Hindi songs and provides a free tier with ad-supported access to music.\n\n2. **Gaana**: Similar to JioSaavn, Gaana offers a wide range of Hindi songs and has a free tier with ads.\n\n3. **YouTube**: Many artists and music labels upload their music videos and songs on YouTube, and you can listen to them for free, although downloading would require using third-party tools or services.\n\n4. **Hungama**: Hungama provides a substantial library of Hindi music and has free streaming options.\n\nRemember, downloading music for offline use without proper authorization can infringe on copyright laws. It's always best to support artists by using legitimate streaming services or purchasing their music.",
